Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,(在老公的面前被侵犯)\N(被欺騙的年輕人妻)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,美穗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的購房安排
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一年的消費這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,五年後然後這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,十年這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然後是伙食費 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話 存款
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.46,0:01:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-感覺不錯?\N-不是 完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不存多一點 這個\N你也想有自己的房子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.76,0:01:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不是租房子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去上班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 這個不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你在家裡應該\N好好的支持我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼說來 美穗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,解決這個問題只有一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我出來創業
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:01:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 直樹\N我還是出來上班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,美穗 我們說好了\N十年後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要回來自己的家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-那麼我走了-慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,十年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,十年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,十年後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,(在家兼職)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,(協助老公)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,(一次千元的電子券)\N(無風險)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,(三十多家嚴選推薦商家)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,(電話面試 極其安全)\N(本人照片驗證）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,午安 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 很緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有關係的，放鬆一點\N我先來簡單的問一下你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,家庭成員還有愛好等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:05:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-有我和老公兩人\N-有孩子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 吃這麽好\N要花不少錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有關係 偶爾一次而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣能夠補充更多營養
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,直樹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,美穗昨晚的晚飯\N雖然非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-但是太過浪費了 -抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我們忍耐十年吧 為了\N我們兩人的家加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好的加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-我走了 -慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,十年 十年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,十年後 我多少歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是在這之前生孩子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,(投資的公司倒閉了)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,(申請五千萬貸款)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我的社保號碼KY92900
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,請您通過我的貸款吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有專門的倒閉貸款服務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我會還的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-是不是其他用途 -沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也有可能利用協力廠商確認
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你能夠提供什麼擔保嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我們所有貸款以及後果\N均由客人自主承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,您的貸款金額五千萬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有其他要求\N我應該可以提供
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也需要看到信用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,求您幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是不能幫忙\N我們需要通過網路瞭解您的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,您的手機必須安裝\N我們指定的軟體並聯網
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,現在上面瞭解 您在家嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,本人確認結束 那麼\N接下來開始瞭解資料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來\N做好了窖人的資料了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,公司保密的 我們需要\N進一步評估客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己不太懂這個\N不知道需要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有關係 其他的交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都順利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,忍耐十年 買一套小房子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,也不能說沒有風險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己好好想想\N自己應該怎麼樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易來到這裡\N我來詳細問一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這是緊張的皮膚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼可憐的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,老公沒有這樣摸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,已經忘了做愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,都是自己一個人\N一直做家庭主婦 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧 慢慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好好觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,記得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,結婚之前的歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,和老公完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,和他沒有做愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很期待想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想逃離嗎?要逃離嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有關係 想逃離的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣回去鄉下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是很想喊救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,也許會有人來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喊救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,也許有人來救你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不想被救是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡裸體讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,誰會來救你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,想喊救命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是好興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,跑到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好興奮吧 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好好回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心的做愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要發出叫聲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是好硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣手指進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣濕漉漉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是很想要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼棣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,進去裡面了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,來這樣來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,激烈一點是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,還不夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,來 不是很濕了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.26,0:23:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,來繼續啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.43,0:24:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服吧 來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.93,0:24:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.90,0:24:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.60,0:24:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.40,0:25:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,插進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.90,0:25:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吧 忘了嗎?這個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.76,0:25:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,握住
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.93,0:25:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼表情 來 含住
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.00,0:25:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.96,0:25:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.43,0:26:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.10,0:26:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人也開心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.60,0:26:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.70,0:26:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.73,0:26:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.50,0:26:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,含住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.96,0:27:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是好興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.66,0:27:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人的愛液全部塗抹上去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.96,0:27:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,還是第一次這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.03,0:27:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,來 繼續 張開嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.36,0:28:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,還想要更多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.80,0:28:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,插進去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.40,0:29:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可以大餮叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.63,0:30:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.93,0:30:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.53,0:31:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好好張開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.83,0:31:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡想要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.60,0:32:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.73,0:33:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢的可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.56,0:33:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小穴非常棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.30,0:34:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.36,0:34:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,直接這樣射進去裡面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.10,0:34:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.43,0:34:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-不行啊\N-平時沒有射進去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.69,0:34:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,來了啊 好好射進去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.86,0:34:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.26,0:35:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話可能再省一點更好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.56,0:36:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也經過了一年時間了\N應該多少會存點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.16,0:36:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊 也不知道好還是不好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.53,0:36:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這個也只是當做目標\N目前努力的一個目標而已
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.60,0:36:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 你覺得怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.36,0:36:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 沒有聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.53,0:36:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,買了化妝品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.36,0:37:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,娜皮膚都變了 感覺你皮膚\N變得更加水嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.43,0:37:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要亂花錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.16,0:37:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-好的 -我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.06,0:37:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.70,0:37:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我想通過視頻看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.33,0:38:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你的美貌和年輕\N讓愚蠢的老公浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.50,0:38:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.50,0:38:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想使用你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.03,0:38:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可憐的鈴木
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.56,0:38:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,張開眼睛張開眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.20,0:40:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我來教導你這具身軀\N為了金錢 還需要付出更多
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.60,0:40:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不僅僅是壓抑的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.70,0:40:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,也不僅僅是成為有錢人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.10,0:40:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,即便很貧窮
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.00,0:40:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也有努力活著的人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.06,0:40:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,最為重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.50,0:40:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人未習慣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.06,0:40:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說那種沒有\N傾述對象的人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.63,0:41:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.56,0:41:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看著我的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.13,0:41:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,自己的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.93,0:42:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,來接下來彌
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.56,0:42:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,變得更加漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.60,0:42:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,更加
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.83,0:42:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮的皮膚
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.50,0:42:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,來看著我這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.06,0:42:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭繼續伸出來一點
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.36,0:43:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 感覺到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.70,0:43:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,來自己看看舔著的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.26,0:43:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,乳頭也是硬硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.46,0:43:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有試過這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.76,0:43:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一直很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.76,0:43:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡已經濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.66,0:44:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜歡這樣是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.23,0:44:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是不僅僅是忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.96,0:44:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,無需忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.50,0:44:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看看這麼多出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.73,0:44:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒吧 想我舔這裡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.73,0:44:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,舔了哦全部
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.36,0:44:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,對了張開
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.43,0:45:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了 自己摸的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.23,0:45:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.26,0:45:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,放鬆一點
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.63,0:46:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊 好舒服是吧\N說一下舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.16,0:46:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,淫蕩的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.00,0:47:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.16,0:47:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,來 在裡面轉圈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.96,0:47:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣伸進去裡面\N想插道去想得不得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.96,0:47:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,漸漸濕漉漉的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.93,0:47:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.96,0:48:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊 來
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.43,0:48:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,兩邊一起玩弄好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.46,0:48:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.46,0:49:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真的非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.56,0:49:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,老公沒有舔過這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.10,0:49:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,自己抬起腰來
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.03,0:50:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了哦 你的小穴\N到屁眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.60,0:50:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看著好興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.83,0:51:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這個地方沒有舔過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.93,0:51:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.20,0:52:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.16,0:52:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,來來
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.00,0:52:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣是吧來
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.80,0:52:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續是吧 繼續是吧來
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.06,0:52:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.73,0:53:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.93,0:53:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.63,0:53:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,過來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.20,0:53:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.26,0:54:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭舔著我的乳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.93,0:54:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,用舌頭舔著
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.46,0:54:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.16,0:54:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好擅辰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.33,0:54:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 手動起來摸我肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.30,0:55:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,來 做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.56,0:55:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 就是這樣口交
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.06,0:55:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,含住舔著
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.26,0:56:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,出來很多唾夜
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.13,0:56:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,聲音也非常享受
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.46,0:56:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.10,0:56:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋蛋也想舔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.60,0:56:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.76,0:56:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.80,0:57:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,超級舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.36,0:57:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.50,0:57:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,手和嘴兩個都要動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.60,0:58:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 好擅長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.03,0:58:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,漸漸激烈一點可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.73,0:58:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 就是這樣合住\N繼續激烈一點
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.73,0:59:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡哦怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.26,0:59:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,想要是吧 來 自己過來
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.66,0:59:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 不想插進去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.30,1:00:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 就是保持這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.40,1:00:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,過來這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.63,1:00:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,自己插進去了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.40,1:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.56,1:00:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,自己怎麼樣舒服 怎麼樣動起來
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.80,1:00:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣 腰轉圈
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.16,1:01:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,腰前後扭動 摩擦陰核
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.16,1:01:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣 這樣動起來
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.73,1:01:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這個感覺怎麼樣啊\N舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.40,1:01:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,跪下來
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.76,1:01:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.66,1:01:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 前後動起來對了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.26,1:02:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,進去裡面了哦\N裡面好舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.76,1:02:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.80,1:02:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊 自己怎麼樣舒服\N怎麼樣做
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.70,1:02:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可以跪下來啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.00,1:02:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.83,1:02:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,摩擦好舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.76,1:03:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續動起來
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.46,1:03:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 繼續繼續
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.70,1:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.26,1:05:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,來 動起來啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.76,1:05:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,全部插進去
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.83,1:06:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,想要更加舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.23,1:06:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,腰抬起來 對了 繼續
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.66,1:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,緊緊的夾住了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.30,1:07:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-頂到裡面了吧\N-不行 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.03,1:07:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,摩擦裡面 好舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.96,1:08:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,還想要繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.63,1:08:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,還不夠是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.36,1:08:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 想殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.96,1:08:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了我 沒有錢啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.89,1:09:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果這樣你開心
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.46,1:09:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就插下來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.56,1:09:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.46,1:09:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,美穗
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.93,1:09:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,美穗?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.36,1:09:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 求你了 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.93,1:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你這樣貧窮的人\N夫人不想再過了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.80,1:09:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,說想出去外面工作
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.10,1:10:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是一直忍著
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.16,1:10:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.20,1:10:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,做了好吃的 買了化妝品
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.13,1:10:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,還有做愛
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.36,1:10:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你要忍耐到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.86,1:10:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,十年後 夫人的身體\N內心會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.50,1:10:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人多少歲了?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.30,1:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,錢方面就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.76,1:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我會給你介紹更好的項目
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.26,1:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只是不能有任何反抗哦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.63,1:10:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,作為代價
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.46,1:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,需要犧牲一點點啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.56,1:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可以支付一大筆錢哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.70,1:11:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,來 好好期待吧 好好期待
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.66,1:11:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在老公面前
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.86,1:11:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢的 好好的\N玩弄你這個淫蕩的樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.40,1:11:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看你真實淫蕩的樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.33,1:11:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.20,1:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,讓稱老公也享受下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.46,1:11:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.10,1:12:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,對著你老公那邊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.16,1:12:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人一直在忍耐啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.66,1:13:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,來 弄一個害羞的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.30,1:13:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.73,1:13:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.56,1:13:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,已經濕了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.36,1:13:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在老公面前
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.56,1:13:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續讓他看看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.43,1:13:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.63,1:13:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,來老公聽到聲音了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.63,1:13:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,來 濕漉漉的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.00,1:14:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的 叫出來
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.60,1:14:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.70,1:14:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續 繼續讓禰興奮\N讓老公看著你的樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.50,1:14:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 已經這樣了來
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.60,1:15:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,讓老公看看
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.26,1:15:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.76,1:15:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.43,1:15:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他看著後面吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.06,1:15:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.16,1:16:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,來 讓老公看看
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.06,1:16:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣是吧 怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.33,1:17:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,漸漸濕漉漉的了\N非常不錯哦夫入
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.36,1:17:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很不錯哦 夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.20,1:17:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看到整個屁眼了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.46,1:17:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,老公在看著哦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.60,1:17:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,來 繼續叫啊 繼續
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.86,1:18:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來 好好說 知道吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.53,1:18:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.73,1:18:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,來高潮了是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.76,1:18:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你老公明白
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.63,1:18:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.96,1:19:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.36,1:19:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看看啊 來 接下來舔一下
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.50,1:19:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,想舔是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.60,1:19:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人的汁液好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.83,1:20:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼漂亮的陰核
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.36,1:20:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.13,1:21:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡 想要我的肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.46,1:21:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是 來
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.80,1:21:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是一直很想要肉棒\N想要得不得了把 夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.50,1:21:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 漸漸濕漉漉的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.80,1:22:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.00,1:23:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的表情很想要的樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.63,1:23:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.86,1:23:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我來教稱
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.76,1:23:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,舔我的身體吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.13,1:23:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.70,1:23:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,五千萬
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.16,1:23:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人 讓我舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.16,1:24:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.50,1:24:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舔我好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.53,1:24:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.90,1:25:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.46,1:26:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣摸一下
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.46,1:26:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不好好弄 是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.33,1:26:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人的嘴裡真的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.76,1:27:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.06,1:29:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.86,1:29:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人 激烈一點
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.00,1:30:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.96,1:30:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想要這個是不是
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.56,1:30:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,首先啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.63,1:30:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴弄到我的臉上
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.53,1:30:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我來舔
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.00,1:31:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的表情是不是高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.06,1:31:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.03,1:32:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎?夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.16,1:32:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,老公好好看著
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.90,1:32:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這根肉棒不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.46,1:33:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.36,1:33:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人的叫聲太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.60,1:34:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服吧 夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.80,1:35:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.53,1:35:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.96,1:35:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,跟教你一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.56,1:35:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,到上面來 我躺下來
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.43,1:36:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,來來
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.06,1:36:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,跪下來 讓你老公好好看看
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.66,1:36:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.16,1:38:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看著老公
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.36,1:39:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.13,1:39:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,說一下舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.70,1:39:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,說一下
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.23,1:39:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,說啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.46,1:39:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.00,1:39:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.83,1:39:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.40,1:39:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.23,1:39:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,射進去裡面的感覺\N讓你老公好好看看
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.43,1:39:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,說一下射進去裡面
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.93,1:40:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,說啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.56,1:40:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,射進去裡面
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.16,1:40:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有聽到 讓你老公聽到
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.46,1:40:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,射進去裡面
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.70,1:40:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,射進去裡面
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.80,1:40:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,射進去裡面
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.70,1:40:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,來了哦 好好射進去裡面
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.63,1:41:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.96,1:41:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.03,1:42:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,來 來